items.badge_description: While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 290 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 59!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 410 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 83!
